ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, it is a useful course.
Sure--it's a good seminar class with lots of interesting and varied material.
very interesting course. good subject material. I wish a few more students had signed up for the course so that there could be more focus on discussion

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: It gave me more idea in AGI.

I learned a lot about various subtopics in AGI as well as the current state of AGI research. I'm unlikely to make much use of this information in a professional context, but it's still interesting to think about and discuss.
